==Getting started==
===Talking to King Vargas===
* '''King Vargas:''' Who are you? Who seeks audience with the King of this fair land of Miscellania?
* '''Player:''' I am known in these lands as [Fremennik name], Your Majesty. I come in search of a quest.
* '''King Vargas:''' Ah, it pleases me to see such enthusiasm!
* '''King Vargas:''' I was once an adventurer such as yourself; even while fulfilling my duties as King of Miscellania, I would roam the lands in search of adventure, and strike down mighty foes with a single blow!
* '''King Vargas:''' Unfortunately, I was a little too daring, and attempted to brave the icelands, where I finally met my match.
* '''King Vargas:''' I survived, barely, but I was cursed for the rest of my life to stay in this form. Which leaves me incapable of performing my duties as ruler.
* '''King Vargas:''' This is why I am looking for an exceptional soul to be regent of this fair kingdom of Miscellania.
* {{tselect|Start the Throne of Miscellania quest?}}
* {{topt|Yes.}}
** '''Player:''' If I may be so bold, Your Majesty, I think Miscellania would rest in capable hands with me.
** '''King Vargas:''' Hahaha! You are bold, [Fremennik name], but then I have yet to see a good ruler who was not.
** '''King Vargas:''' You will first have to demonstrate your worth. You are a good warrior, that I do not doubt; however ruling also requires a good grasp of diplomacy.
** '''King Vargas:''' We have been at war with neighbouring Etceteria for hundreds of years; however, I think both of us have rather lost our appetite for hostilities.
** '''King Vargas:''' Now may be an opportune time to make amends. If you manage to negotiate peace with them, then you will truly have shown your skill as a diplomat.
** '''Player:''' Then do not stray far, Your Majesty, for I shall soon return.
** '''King Vargas:''' Wait! There is one more matter to discuss... a mere formality, of course.
** '''King Vargas:''' By Miscellanious tradition, one may not become regent of the kingdom unless in the trust of the royal family.
** '''King Vargas:''' This includes that of the future king or queen. It is yet too early for me to decide which of my children should inherit the throne.
** '''King Vargas:''' Until then, gaining the trust of one of them should suffice. Who knows? Your choice might help me make a decision later.
** '''King Vargas:''' So tell me! Which of my children will you attempt to gain the trust of?
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|I want to earn Prince Brand's approval.}}
*** '''Player:''' I would like to choose Prince Brand.
*** '''Player:''' And you say this is a mere formality, Your Majesty?
*** '''King Vargas:''' I am sure you can form a good working relationship with him. You can ask Ghrim for advice; that's what he's here for, after all.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|I want to earn Princess Astrid's approval.}}
*** '''Player:''' I would like to choose Princess Astrid.
*** '''Player:''' And you say this is a mere formality, Your Majesty?
*** '''King Vargas:''' I am sure you can form a good working relationship with her. You can ask Ghrim for advice; that's what he's here for, after all.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|No.}}
** '''Player:''' I'm afraid I must decline, Your Majesty. The call of adventure is too strong for me to accept a sedentary life.
** '''King Vargas:''' I can assure you that I managed to heed that same call, and ruling this land was no hindrance to me. However, I understand your decision. Fare thee well!
** {{tact|end}}

